$ HA144A - Forward Swept Wing (FSW) Static Aeroelastic Trim
$ MSC Nastran Aeroelastic User Guide Example HA144A
$ Adapted for NastAero SOL 144
$
$ Half-span model with SYMXZ=1 (image vortices for symmetry)
$ Units: ft-lb-sec. Masses scaled so mass*9.81 = weight_lb
$ Total aircraft weight = 8000 lb
$
SOL 144
CEND
$
TITLE = HA144A FSW STATIC AEROELASTIC TRIM
SPC = 1
TRIM = 1
DISPLACEMENT = ALL
$
